   Manning, J. C., Univ KwaZulu Nata Pietermaritzburg, Res Ctr Plant Growth \& Dev, Sch Biol \& Conservadon Sci, ZA-3209 Scottsville, South Africa.
   Goldblatt, P., Missouri Bot Garden, St Louis, MO 63166 USA.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.sajb.2011.02.008},
