   Roguz, Katarzyna; Gallagher, M. Kate; Senden, Esther; Bar-Lev, Yamit; Lebel, Merav; Heliczer, Roni; Sapir, Yuval, Tel Aviv Univ, Sch Plant Sci, Tel Aviv, Israel.
   Roguz, Katarzyna, Univ Warsaw, Fac Biol, Warsaw, Poland.},
